@startuml fig-packet-capture-workflow
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
title Flux de Captura si Analiza Pachete

start
:Porneste captura\ntcpdump -i any -w demo.pcap;
:Genereaza trafic\nClient/Server TCP, Emitator UDP;
:Opreste captura\nCtrl+C;
:Analizeaza cu tshark\ntshark -r demo.pcap;
:Filtreaza trafic specific\ntshark -Y "tcp.port==9090";
:Extrage campuri\ntshark -T fields\n-e ip.src -e tcp.flags;
:Genereaza statistici\ntshark -q -z conv,tcp;
:Documenteaza dovezi\nSalveaza pcap + loguri;
stop

legend right
Flag-uri tcpdump:
-i any : toate interfetele
-nn : fara rezolutie DNS
-w fisier : scrie in pcap
-U : output nebuferat

Filtre tshark:
-Y : filtru afisare
-T fields : format iesire
-q -z : mod statistici
endlegend
@enduml
